data.description:
Beautiful updated home featuring bamboo flooring in the formal living, dining and powder room. Hardwood floors in stair case and all of upstairs, upgraded fixtures, ceramic tile and upgraded counter tops in the kitchen which is open to the den. Upstairs has a large master with master bath and a WIC, plus living room with office/work area, another full bath and 2 additional bedrooms. This home also features upgraded front and rear doors, coated garage floor, and a nice size back yard for kids to play. Home is in a quiet area of Harriet Creek Ranch subdivision In sought-after Northwest ISD Schools. Close to Elementary, Middle and High Schools. Subdivision offers community pools, play areas and walking trails.

Must have Income greater than 3x rent, Credit above 600 and good rental history.
